&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bring the Olives&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;- we offer premium customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Think Big&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;- we believe in always striving for more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced brand leader to synthesize everything we&#39;ve learned to date, from creative development to player feedback into a refined global master brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will bring together insights, research, and stakeholder perspectives from across Betty.ca to define a clear, scalable brand framework. The long-term goal is to establish how Betty shows up consistently across markets, products, and customer touchpoints, while continuing to evolve and strengthen the Betty.ca brand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop further the brand&#39;s identity and positioning in the market through tone, storytelling, and visuals across all channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead creative campaigns end to end, from concept through production and launch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build creative systems and templates that enable the team to produce on-brand work at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data and analytics to inform creative briefs and measure brand impact, adjusting based on what works&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with growth, product, marketing, and local market leaders to align creative with business priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track brand adherence and health, and report visibility to leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure brand and creative meet responsible-gambling and regulatory requirements across all markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and grow a high-performing creative team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we&#39;re looking for: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years in brand &amp;amp; creative strategy, marketing leadership, or brand architecture roles, with experience leading or redefining global brand systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to collect and synthesize complex brand and research input into actionable frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong qualitative and quantitative brand research experience (player insights, market trends, positioning validation)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and facilitation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience balancing creative vision with operational process and governance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
